1474
01:11:44,467 --> 01:11:45,798
What am I walking into?

1475
01:11:45,886 --> 01:11:47,267
What are you walking into?

1476
01:11:47,345 --> 01:11:48,977
Yes, what the fuck is going on?!

1477
01:11:49,056 --> 01:11:52,689
