about being surprised about LA.

1488
01:12:12,495 --> 01:12:14,157
Surprise! I have my own opinions.

1489
01:12:14,247 --> 01:12:16,409
How do you even know
how to do something like that?

1490
01:12:16,499 --> 01:12:18,461
