2214
01:48:02,977 --> 01:48:03,978
Shall we go in here?

2215
01:48:04,270 --> 01:48:05,271
Sure.

2216
01:48:12,112 --> 01:48:13,113
Um...

2217
01:48:22,455 --> 01:48:25,378
Um, what's a day like
for the two of you here?

2218
01:48:25,916 --> 01:48:28,209
Well, if he has school,
I take him there, of course,

2219
01:48:28,294 --> 01:48:30,336
and pick him up, assuming I can do both.

2220
01:48:30,588 --> 01:48:32,720
What prevents you from picking him up?

2221
01:48:33,007 --> 01:48:34,008
