2248
01:49:43,911 --> 01:49:46,334
And so, we go there.
And then, afterwards...

2249
01:49:47,290 --> 01:49:50,793
maybe we'll get lunch somewhere,
and then, if there's a movie to see...

2250
01:49:51,043 --> 01:49:52,665
Does he like basketball?

2251
01:49:52,753 --> 01:49:53,754
He does.

2252
01:49:53,963 --> 01:49:57,337
His coach, uh, Rick, says
he's a good dribbler, and I've seen that.

2253
01:49:57,800 --> 01:49:58,971
