- Ron.

2254
01:49:59,802 --> 01:50:01,764
Sorry, his coach's name is Ron.

2255
01:50:01,846 --> 01:50:03,348
Rick's his dentist in New York.

2256
01:50:03,431 --> 01:50:06,644
Well, you know our home home was...
