2259
01:50:10,813 --> 01:50:12,565
Well, we like it because we can walk.

2260
01:50:12,648 --> 01:50:14,150
You can walk here.

2261
01:50:14,525 --> 01:50:15,526
Not really.

2262
01:50:15,568 --> 01:50:17,029
And the space...

2263
01:50:23,409 --> 01:50:24,790
Do you like your school?

2264
01:50:25,745 --> 01:50:26,746
I love it.

2265
01:50:27,079 --> 01:50:29,202
