2267
01:50:32,168 --> 01:50:33,169
Maybe gym.

2268
01:50:33,461 --> 01:50:34,672
You like math.

2269
01:50:35,838 --> 01:50:36,959
Not anymore.

2270
01:50:38,758 --> 01:50:39,959
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

2271
